# Character Creation

The party must decide collectively what universe to start in. Use the corresponding homebrew.
Start on level 1. Make sure you give me lots of NPCs to kill off in your backstory.
Use the extra ability scores of sanity. also add the extra intelligence based skills of: 

* science
* technology
* piloting
* Riddle
* and tradition

You can have guns even if you start of in middle-earth or the forgoten realms I don't care. You can use the Gunslinger subclass if you want.